  "texts": [
    "The current work adds to the literature available on these problems by proposing a unique framework that makes use of deep learning for accurate forecasting and recommender systems for tailored retention strategies, fine-tuned to the needs.",
    "In this research work, novel deep learning-based approach has been introduced for student enrolment prediction.",
    "In addition, the reinforcement learning has been utilized for retention recommendation.",
    "The architecture of the proposed model is shown in Fig. 1.",
    "• Objective: Design a system that will not only allow for the prediction of future student enrollments but also give recommendations on personalized strategies in relation to student retention and improved academic performance."
  ]
}